quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  6,69,"Fawaaki gom…óu…ìe huli Alla …ìen rentii e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, hay huunde e √±aawoore too√±u…ìe …ìen. Ko fawii …ìe, ko ha…óugol …ìe e faggitagol bone, belajo'o,…ìe hulay Alla, …ìe rentoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  6,70,"An Nulaa…óo, terto …ìee sirkoo…ìe wa…ótir…ìe diina mun kan jalnori e mbelee…óe, nguurndam aduna …óam kadi hodi …ìe. Waajor yim…ìe …ìen an Annabaajo on, ndee Qur'aanaare, fii wata wonkii jebbilinire halkaare sabu ko ki faggitii kon e bakkaatu. Alanaa ki gaanin Alla gi…óo walloowo wanaa kadi tefanoo…óo …ìe lepte laakara …óen ; hay si tawii non ki sottorii kala sottorgal, ki ja…ìantaake …óum. Ko …ìen …óon woni jebbiliniraa…ìe halkaare, sabu kon ko …ìe faggitii e geddi. Hino woodani …ìe √ëalnde Darngal, njaram wul…óam e lepte muusu…óe, sabu ko …ìe yeddi kon."
  6,71,"Maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe an Nulaa…óo : "E men reway gaanin Alla sanamuuji …ói nafataa men kadi …ói lorrataa men, men murta gaay e gom…óinal ngal …ìaawo nde Alla fewnude men, men wona wa on seytaane majjini, o tertodi mo e weemugol, hara on no jogii wondii…ìe feewu…ìe …ìe no noddira mo goonga, kono o saloo nootagol ndun noddaandu ma…ì…ìe? Maakan …ìe : "Pellet, peewal Alla ngal, ko ngal woni peewal goonga. Alla yamirii men jebbilanagol Mo Kanko Senii…óo On, men bajjin…óinira Mo, men rewa Mo, ko Kanko woni Joomiiko Winndere nden."
  6,72,"O yamirii men kadi √±ii…ìnugol julde nden no haaniri, e hulugol Mo √±emtina yamiraa…ói Makko rentoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko. Ko Kano woni On Mo jeyaa…ìe …ìen moo…ìoytee ka Mun √ëalnde Darngal no O yo…ìitira …ìe njo…ìdi golle ma…ì…ìe."
  6,73,"Ko Kanko Senii…óo On woni tagir…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin goonga. √ëalnde Alla Daalanoyta huunde nden : "Laato!" : nde laatoo. Tuma O Daaloyta √ëalnde Darngal : "Immee!", …ìe immoo. Daalol Makko ngol ko laatoray ngol goonga. Ko Kanko Senii…óo On tun laamu woodani √ëalnde Darngal tuma Asraafiilu wuttoyta …óimmun ka alaadu. Ko O Anndu…óo ko wirnii e ko fee√±i. Ko O √ëee√±u…óo e tagu Makko ngun e toppitagol Mo ngol, Humpitii…óo kala huunde."